Author: skelekey
Text: Cellulite probably has nothing to do with this, it’s about how the fat is stored on the body and forms “bubbles”.  Unless you’re eating a diet high in unhealthy fats, no fiber, and not exercising at all, it’s probably just because of your body. Sometimes cellulite can even appear AFTER losing weight.
